OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA cloudy
OL,6,Fevening with patchy rain across
OL,7,FArgyll. Otherwise, a dry and bright
OL,8,Fend to the day, then dry with
OL,9,Flengthening clear spells overnight.
OL,10,FLight southwesterly winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CMonday:FA largely dry day with plenty
OL,13,Fof sunshine and feeling warm. Cloudier
OL,14,Fwith patchy rain across Argyll. Warm
OL,15,Fin the sunshine.
